# KinderLight RGB - Rear PCB - Netlist

# Power nets
Net "VIN_12V"         -> Input 12V (External)
Net "5V_OUT"          -> Buck Converter output -> ESP32 VCC, Front PCB via JST
Net "GND"             -> Common Ground everywhere

# Buck Converter
VIN_12V -> DC1 Input +
GND     -> DC1 Input -

DC1 Output + (5V) -> ESP32 VCC
DC1 Output - (GND) -> System GND

# ESP32 Power
ESP32 VCC -> 5V
ESP32 GND -> GND

# Serial/Debug Connection from Front
J3 Pin1 (GND)         -> GND
J3 Pin2 (TX Front)    -> ESP32 RX
J3 Pin3 (RX Front)    -> ESP32 TX
J3 Pin4 (DTR Front)   -> ESP32 EN (Reset)
J3 Pin5 (RTS Front)   -> ESP32 BOOT (GPIO9)

# Internal Serial Connector (ESP32 Debug)
J4 Pin1 (GND)         -> GND
J4 Pin2 (TX ESP32)    -> ESP32 TX
J4 Pin3 (RX ESP32)    -> ESP32 RX
J4 Pin4 (DTR ESP32)   -> ESP32 EN
J4 Pin5 (RTS ESP32)   -> ESP32 BOOT (GPIO9)

# Battery Backup (optional)
BAT_CONN + -> VCC (through diode if needed)
BAT_CONN - -> GND

# Tag-Connect Programming (Optional)
Pads arranged for Tag-Connect TC2030 footprint to ESP32 serial lines + reset.
